Class BigdataTurtleWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openrdf.rio.helpers.RDFWriterBase

        • com.bigdata.rdf.rio.turtle.BigdataTurtleWriter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.openrdf.rio.RDFHandler, org.openrdf.rio.RDFWriter

    public class BigdataTurtleWriter
extends org.openrdf.rio.turtle.TurtleWriter
implements org.openrdf.rio.RDFWriter
    An implementation of the RDFWriter interface that writes RDF documents in Turtle format. The Turtle format is defined in in this document.
